{"data":[{"date":"18:22 11/07","title":"S\u1ebfp Juventus ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/marotta-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-cach-chieu-mo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Marotta ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo, b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d c\u1ee7a Juventus m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mua Joao Cancelo ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ecb thu h\u00fat.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-real-xac-nhan-ronaldo-cap-ben-juventus-180-190888.html\" target=\"_blank\"><br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Juventus</span> v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0 k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 4 n\u0103m, m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a CLB. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Bianconeri \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng CR7, Joao Cancelo t\u1eeb Valencia v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 40,4 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u nghi v\u1ea5n xung quanh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Juventus mua Cancelo. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i cho Inter Milan d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u. Trong khi Nerazzurri kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u1ee9t Cancelo th\u00ec \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd t\u1ea1i Serie A l\u1ea1i chi r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eadm cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marotta ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo, b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng bom t\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a Juve h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Marotta ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo, b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng bom t\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a Juve h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Marotta-phat-bieu-ve-Ronaldo,-ban-hop-dong-bom-tan-cua-Juve-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edbi th\u1ea1o tin cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c Juventus mua Cancelo, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Jorge Mendes v\u1edbi Ronaldo l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u00f2ng ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c, sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Marotta ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed m\u1eadt</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n t\u1edd Corriere della Sera, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Juventus, Giuseppe Marotta ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo. \u00d4ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 chi ti\u1ebft qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d v\u1edbi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cancelo va Ronaldo\" title=\"Cancelo va Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/marotta-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-cach-chieu-mo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Marotta ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t x\u00fac t\u00e1c Cancelo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac\u201d, Marotta n\u00f3i. \u201cNh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3ng qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Juventus. Cristiano Ronaldo l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1ecdn Juventus l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKhi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn ra r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1eafm b\u1eaft c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 cho CLB. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Cancelo, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Jorge Mendes nh\u01b0 Ronaldo. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n Ronaldo h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u00e0 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i khi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 gia nh\u1eadp Juventus.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cRonaldo s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t vui khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i cho m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng CLB l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd s\u1ed1ng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u0103n penthouse tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p \u1edf trung t\u00e2m th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Turin.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/infographics/infographics-cristiano-ronaldo-chia-tay-real-madrid-ra-di-de-lai-nhung-gi-406-190961.html\">Infographics: Cristiano Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid - Ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/pele-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-quyet-dinh-sang-juventus-180-190910.html\">\u201cVua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1\u201d Pele ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-kiem-duoc-bao-nhieu-tu-thuong-vu-real-ban-ronaldo-cho-juventus-172-190891.html\">M.U ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao nhi\u00eau t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Real b\u00e1n Ronaldo cho Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/cristiano-ronaldo-gui-tam-thu-day-xuc-dong-toi-real-madrid-180-190889.html\">Cristiano Ronaldo g\u1eedi t\u00e2m th\u01b0 \u0111\u1ea7y x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1edbi Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4147","checkdouble":"190965"},{"date":"18:55 11/07","title":"Barca c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua sao PSG","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/3/28/Tien-ve-Adrien-Rabiot-muon-toi-Anh-trong-tuong-lai-gan-hinh-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, theo Mundo Deportivo, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca nh\u1eafm Adrien Rabiot n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecbu nh\u1eefng t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. Andres Iniesta \u0111\u00e3 chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng sau nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/8/Barca-muon-mua-Adrien-Rabiot-voi-gia-35-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Rabiot</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-paulinho-roi-barca-chi-sau-11-thang-180-190739.html\" target=\"_blank\">Paulinho l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay Barca</span>. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u H\u1eb1ng \u0110\u1ea1i. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Iniesta v\u00e0 Paulinho, tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Barca \u0111ang r\u1ea5t m\u1ecfng, HLV Ernesto Valverde \u0111ang \u01b0u ti\u00ean n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, HLV Valverde \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Camp Nou.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Mundo Deportivo, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i. \u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c PSG b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 La Liga ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Rabiot\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, Adrien Rabiot \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o PSG. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 47 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua sao PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Barca c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua sao PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/3/28/Tien-ve-Adrien-Rabiot-muon-toi-Anh-trong-tuong-lai-gan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Rabiot\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng, m\u00f9a 2017/18 anh ghi 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 7 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. Tuy nhi\u00ean, vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a anh d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Thomas Tuchel c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u HLV Dortmund \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ec3 Julian Draxler \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Marco Verratti v\u00e0 Thiago Motta, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRabiot s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi HLV Tuchel, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd r\u1eddi s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed. N\u1ebfu Barca ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho Adrien Rabiot m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 kh\u00e1\u00a0cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4146","checkdouble":"190971"},{"date":"19:11 11/07","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! 3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real nh\u1eafm thay Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/day-3-muc-tieu-hang-dau-duoc-real-nham-thay-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111ang \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Cristiano Ronaldo, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Los Blancos.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00f4m qua, Real Madrid ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus. Theo \u0111\u00f3, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1985 \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi, sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 nh\u1eafm 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thay Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 nh\u1eafm 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thay Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Chuyen-nhuong-Real-Madrid-2018-nham-3-cau-thu-thay-Ronaldo-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real \u0111ang t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCR7 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin, anh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng 30 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Higuain \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 Serie A.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Los Blancos.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Sports Illustrated, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez \u0111ang g\u1ea5p r\u00fat t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Los Blancos s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real nh\u1eafm thay Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111ang \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Cristiano Ronaldo, 3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm bao g\u1ed3m Neymar, Kylian Mbappe v\u00e0 Eden Hazard.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe khong hai long voi Neymar\" title=\"Mbappe kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi Neymar\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/day-3-muc-tieu-hang-dau-duoc-real-nham-thay-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mbappe v\u00e0 Neymar l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Los Blancos c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Chelsea v\u00e0 PSG \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNeymar v\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe m\u1edbi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn PSG \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 400 tri\u1ec7u euro cho Neymar v\u00e0 290 tri\u1ec7u euro cho Mbappe, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Real ph\u1ea3i l\u1eafc \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/hazard-va-asensio-sap-doi-cho-cho-nhau-180-182425.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real mua Hazard thay Ronaldo</span> l\u00e0 s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Bernabeu, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Los Blancos.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Hazard v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2020, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i. N\u1ebfu Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4145","checkdouble":"190973"},{"date":"21:20 11/07","title":"Sau Ronaldo, Real chia tay th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/3/sau-ronaldo-real-chia-tay-them-mot-ngoi-sao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi Real Madrid x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 Ronaldo sang Juve, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chia tay th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao kh\u00e1c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Achraf Hakimi.</h2><h2>Real chia tay Achraf Hakimi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Achraf Hakimi vs Sevilla\" title=\"Achraf Hakimi vs Sevilla\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/10/Nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-huy-diet-cua-Real-truoc-Sevilla-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Achraf Hakimi r\u1eddi Real \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n sang Dortmund thi \u0111\u1ea5u theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang ch\u1ee7 CLB Borussia Dortmund x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i Achraf Hakimi t\u1eeb CLB Real Madrid.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, Hakimi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Dortmund b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi cho \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2019/20.&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau l\u1ec5 k\u00fd k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Hakimi, gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao c\u1ee7a Borussia Dortmund \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Achraf Hakimi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, anh \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i \u1edf b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Real Madrid c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia Morocco&quot;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hakimi n\u0103m nay 19 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 9 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Real Madrid d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Zinedine Zidane \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, ng\u00f4i sao Morocco r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 c\u1ea1nh tranh m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi d\u00e0n sao Real. Do v\u1eady vi\u1ec7c anh ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">BL\u0110 Real c\u0169ng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Dortmund s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 Los Blancos trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Hakimi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Ch\u00e2u Phi, anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i tr\u1ecdn 270 ph\u00fat ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c trong 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u00f3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/day-3-muc-tieu-hang-dau-duoc-real-nham-thay-ronaldo-180-190973.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/day-3-muc-tieu-hang-dau-duoc-real-nham-thay-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/day-3-muc-tieu-hang-dau-duoc-real-nham-thay-ronaldo-180-190973.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! 3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real nh\u1eafm thay Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111ang \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Cristiano Ronaldo, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Los Blancos.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/cristiano-ronaldo-gui-tam-thu-day-xuc-dong-toi-real-madrid-180-190889.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/cristiano-ronaldo-gui-tam-thu-day-xuc-dong-toi-real-madrid-180-190889.html\">Cristiano Ronaldo g\u1eedi t\u00e2m th\u01b0 \u0111\u1ea7y x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1edbi Real Madrid</span><br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 g\u1eedi Real Madrid, t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf t\u00ecnh y\u00eau r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-117-xac-dinh-tuong-lai-gareth-bale-184-190977.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/9/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-117-xac-dinh-tuong-lai-gareth-bale.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-117-xac-dinh-tuong-lai-gareth-bale-184-190977.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 11/7: X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale</span><br>\r\nX\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale, Ed Woodward ch\u1ed1t t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3 cho M.U, Liverpool ra gi\u00e1 cho Messi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4144","checkdouble":"190979"},{"date":"22:44 11/07","title":"Real Madrid s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o sau khi chia tay Ronaldo?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-cau-thu-nao-sau-khi-chia-tay-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Li\u1ec7u Real Madrid s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00e1m v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i? D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng t\u1ecf sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd chia tay si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u1ea3 th\u1ea3y 15 danh hi\u1ec7u, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u00fa hat-trick v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League 'v\u00f4 ti\u1ec1n kho\u1eafng h\u1eadu' trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i Madrid, Ronaldo c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y t\u00e0i s\u0103n b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 450 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 438 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u00ednh trung b\u00ecnh ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 33 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 84 ph\u00fat cho m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Los Blancos.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 huy ho\u00e0ng l\u00e0 v\u1eady nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eb3ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7t ng\u00e3 c\u1ee7a th\u1eddi gian. Sau 9 n\u0103m mi\u1ec7t m\u00e0i c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho Real, s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a Ronaldo c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u01b0 x\u01b0a v\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng HLV Lopetegui l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng s\u00e1t th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi tr\u1ebb kh\u1ecfe h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u1ebf ch\u1ebf m\u1edbi cho ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2u s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ecdn m\u1eb7t g\u1eedi v\u00e0ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi?</p>\r\n<h2>1. Eden Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o sau khi chia tay Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o sau khi chia tay Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Real-Madrid-se-chieu-mo-cau-thu-nao-sau-khi-chia-tay-Ronaldo-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Eden Hazard \u0111ang n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng nh\u1ea5t thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Bernabeu. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a CR7 nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Hazard \u0111ang d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh m\u1edbi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, s\u1ef1 nhanh nh\u1eb9n v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng, ghi b\u00e0n gi\u00fap Hazard l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o 'm\u1eaft xanh' c\u1ee7a BL\u0110 Real. V\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Los Blancos s\u1ebd s\u1edbm th\u1ecfa lu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y, khi m\u00e0 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Hazard v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m.</p>\r\n<h2>2. Neymar</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Neymar c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Real nh\u1eb1m thay th\u1ebf Cristiano Ronaldo. Sinh n\u0103m 1992, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt h\u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi, Neymar \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng l\u00fd cho danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng sau th\u1eddi Ronaldo, Messi.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 li\u1ec7u Neymar c\u00f3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Real v\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n l\u00e0 PSG c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi khi m\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 1 n\u0103m h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf ra kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n l\u00ean t\u1edbi 222 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y k\u00fd v\u1edbi Barcelona.</p>\r\n<h2>3. Kylian Mbappe</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe\" title=\"Mbappe\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Daniel-van-Buyten-phat-bieu-ve-Kylian-Mbappe-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kylian Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t VCK World Cup v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3 v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao n\u0103m nay m\u1edbi 19 tu\u1ed5i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c nhanh nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc xe \u0111ua c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c 1, Mbappe x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u1ebf v\u1ecb Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Bernabeu.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n l\u00e0 PSG s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y khi m\u00e0 t\u1eebng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y t\u1eeb Monaco v\u1edbi chi ph\u00ed t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 180 tri\u1ec7u euro.</p>\r\n<h2>4. Harry Kane</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">4 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y Harry Kane lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e2y s\u0103n b\u00e0n ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a CLB Tottenham khi lu\u00f4n ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi 30 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u1ede hai m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng 2015/16 v\u00e0 2016/17, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u00f2n vinh d\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn danh hi\u1ec7u Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 24, Kane \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i Madrid. Ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 nhanh nh\u1eb9n nh\u01b0 Ronaldo, song anh l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u00e1t th\u1ee7 v\u00f2ng c\u1eafm s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n th\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1eeba.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Real ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i lo chuy\u1ec7n thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, sau khi 'c\u00e2y s\u0103n b\u00e0n' ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c su\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua ra \u0111i.</p>\r\n<h2>5. Robert Lewandowski</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lewandowski lap ky luc\" title=\"Lewandowski l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/6/lewandowski-dung-truoc-ky-luc-moi-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i CLB Bayern Munich c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Real. Tuy nhi\u00ean kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Los Blancos chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Ba Lan l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, khi m\u00e0 anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup v\u1eeba qua.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Lewandowski n\u0103m nay c\u0169ng \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 29 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a H\u00f9m x\u00e1m c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m n\u1eefa.</p>\r\n<h2>6. Mauro Icardi</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Icardi c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau theo \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Real. 29 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i Serie A m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 g\u00e2y thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c HLV Lopetegui. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Icardi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n gi\u00fap CLB Inter Milan tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Champions League khi kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1ea1ng 4 chung cu\u1ed9c.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Icardi c\u00f3 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 110 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 Real ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c anh.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/goc-nhin-cristiano-ronaldo-gia-nhap-juventus-176-190940.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/Gareth-Bale-roi-Real-khong-the-xay-ra-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/goc-nhin-cristiano-ronaldo-gia-nhap-juventus-176-190940.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: V\u00ec b\u1ecb M.U ph\u1ee5 b\u1ea1c, Ronaldo m\u1edbi \u0111i theo \u201cB\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m\u201d Juventus</span><br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, th\u00f4ng tin Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1. \u201cB\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0\u201d kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a CR7 m\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 Man...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sau-ronaldo-real-chia-tay-them-mot-ngoi-sao-180-190979.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/3/sau-ronaldo-real-chia-tay-them-mot-ngoi-sao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sau-ronaldo-real-chia-tay-them-mot-ngoi-sao-180-190979.html\">Sau Ronaldo, Real chia tay th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao</span><br>\r\nSau khi Real Madrid x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 Ronaldo sang Juve, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chia tay th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao kh\u00e1c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Achraf Hakimi.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-duoc-huong-loi-khi-ronaldo-gia-nhap-juventus-172-190982.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/9/20/chelsea-duoc-huong-loi-khi-ronaldo-gia-nhap-juventus.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-duoc-huong-loi-khi-ronaldo-gia-nhap-juventus-172-190982.html\">Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i khi Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus</span><br>\r\nSau khi Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus, CLB Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb L\u00e3o b\u00e0 th\u00e0nh Turin v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 hai ng\u00f4i sao Rugani va\u0300 Higuain.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/day-3-muc-tieu-hang-dau-duoc-real-nham-thay-ronaldo-180-190973.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/day-3-muc-tieu-hang-dau-duoc-real-nham-thay-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/day-3-muc-tieu-hang-dau-duoc-real-nham-thay-ronaldo-180-190973.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! 3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real nh\u1eafm thay Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111ang \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Cristiano Ronaldo, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Los Blancos.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4143","checkdouble":"190984"},{"date":"23:10 11/07","title":"H\u00e9 l\u1ed9 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a Barca trong h\u00e8 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/7/barca-sap-co-tan-binh-thu-hai-trong-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Arthur Melo, CLB Barcelona s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 hai trong \u00edt ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Clement Lenglet t\u1eeb Sevilla.</h2><h2>Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Clement Lenglet</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb t\u1edd Goal, sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian theo \u0111u\u1ed5i, CLB Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Clement Lenglet t\u1eeb Sevilla. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 11/7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Barca.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"N\u00d3NG Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Clement Lenglet h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"N\u00d3NG Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Clement Lenglet h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/6/NONG-Barca-chieu-mo-trung-ve-Clement-Lenglet-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Barca s\u1eafp c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 hai mang t\u00ean Clement Lenglet</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 cho Sevilla\u00a035 tri\u1ec7u euro (31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh), b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00fang s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n trong \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y, sau khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n.\u00a0</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn Champions League, Clement Lenglet \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00e1i t\u00ean hot tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i Barca, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb hai \u00f4ng l\u1edbn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh l\u00e0 M.U v\u00e0 Chelsea. Ngay c\u1ea3 CLB Sevilla c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Lenglet \u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y. Lenglet c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u00e0 anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn Barca.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, Clement Lenglet s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a Barca trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Blaugrana \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i chi ra 40 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2n binh Arthur t\u1eeb Gremio.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-117-xac-dinh-tuong-lai-gareth-bale-184-190977.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/9/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-117-xac-dinh-tuong-lai-gareth-bale.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-117-xac-dinh-tuong-lai-gareth-bale-184-190977.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 11/7: X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale</span><br>\r\nX\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale, Ed Woodward ch\u1ed1t t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3 cho M.U, Liverpool ra gi\u00e1 cho Messi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-cau-thu-nao-sau-khi-chia-tay-ronaldo-180-190984.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-cau-thu-nao-sau-khi-chia-tay-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-cau-thu-nao-sau-khi-chia-tay-ronaldo-180-190984.html\">Real Madrid s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o sau khi chia tay Ronaldo?</span><br>\r\nLi\u1ec7u Real Madrid s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00e1m v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i? D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-duoc-huong-loi-khi-ronaldo-gia-nhap-juventus-172-190982.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/9/20/chelsea-duoc-huong-loi-khi-ronaldo-gia-nhap-juventus.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-duoc-huong-loi-khi-ronaldo-gia-nhap-juventus-172-190982.html\">Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i khi Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus</span><br>\r\nSau khi Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus, CLB Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb L\u00e3o b\u00e0 th\u00e0nh Turin v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 hai ng\u00f4i sao Rugani va\u0300 Higuain.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4142","checkdouble":"190985"},{"date":"19:46 11/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 11/7: X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/9/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-117-xac-dinh-tuong-lai-gareth-bale.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale, Ed Woodward ch\u1ed1t t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3 cho M.U, Liverpool ra gi\u00e1 cho 'Messi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129',... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 11/7.</h2><h2>X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd AS, sau khi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-real-xac-nhan-ronaldo-cap-ben-juventus-180-190888.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay Real Madrid,</span> ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gareth Bale \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua, Bale v\u1eabn s\u1ed1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Ronaldo v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a HLV Lopetegui.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 117 X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 117 X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Diem-tin-bong-da-toi-117-Xac-dinh-tuong-lai-Gareth-Bale-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Bale mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Real sau khi Ronaldo ra \u0111i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>M.U ch\u01b0a h\u1ec1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Rebic</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n CLB Eintracht Frankfurt, Fredi Bobic \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a h\u1ec1 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o t\u1eeb ph\u00eda CLB Man Utd cho tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 24 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia, Ante Rebic.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 gi\u00fap s\u1ee9c c\u00f9ng \u0110T Croatia \u0111i t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup, Rebic \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Ngo\u00e0i M.U th\u00ec c\u1ea3 Arsenal, Tottenham v\u00e0 Napoli c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<h2>Liverpool ra gi\u00e1 cho 'Messi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129'</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Goal.com, CLB Liverpool m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ecfi mua ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed von l\u00e0 'Messi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129', ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xherdan Shaqiri. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh nguy hi\u1ec3m, Shaqiri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung h\u1ee3p l\u00fd tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng The Kop. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft HLV Klopp \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t \u01b0ng ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u00e0nh 13 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mang anh v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Stoke City.</p>\r\n<h2>Ed Woodward ch\u1ed1t t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3 cho M.U</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd Express, do \u00e1p l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3m, Ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Ed Woodward c\u1ee7a Man United \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Toby Alderweireld sau khi x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn anh l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a CLB trong m\u00f9a H\u00e8.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 29 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng Alderweireld v\u1eabn mang \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 y\u00ean t\u00e2m v\u00e0 Man United c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb ngay trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<h2>Liverpool h\u1ecfi mua sao b\u1ef1 PSG</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd The Sun m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecfi mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Grzegorz Krychowiak c\u1ee7a PSG. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung cho tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf sau khi chia tay Emre Can.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 28 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eeb l\u00e2u \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Paris. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, anh chuy\u1ec3n sang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho CLB West Brom d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 31 tr\u1eadn.</p>\r\n<h2>PSG mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu Kante t\u1eeb Chelsea</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a N'golo Kante, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p PSG \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Theo Le10Sport, PSG \u0111\u00e3 coi Kante l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, g\u00e3 nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0u n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho ra kho\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eeb 12 t\u1edbi 15 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a \u0111\u1ec1 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Kante.</p>\r\n<h2>Everton mu\u1ed1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Barca</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin c\u1ee7a Goal, CLB Everton \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi ra 24 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina t\u1eeb Barca. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng t\u1ea1i Nou Camp khi chuy\u1ec3n sang Palmeiras thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng Gi\u00eang v\u1eeba qua.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup gi\u00fap Mina l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o 'm\u1eaft xanh' c\u1ee7a BL\u0110 Everton v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nXem th\u00eam:&nbsp;<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-1007-mu-di-nuoc-co-quan-trong-vu-sao-100-trieu-euro-184-190873.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 10/07: MU \u0111i n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1edd quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1ee5 sao 100 tri\u1ec7u euro<br>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/day-3-muc-tieu-hang-dau-duoc-real-nham-thay-ronaldo-180-190973.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/day-3-muc-tieu-hang-dau-duoc-real-nham-thay-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/day-3-muc-tieu-hang-dau-duoc-real-nham-thay-ronaldo-180-190973.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! 3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real nh\u1eafm thay Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111ang \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Cristiano Ronaldo, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Los Blancos.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/marotta-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-cach-chieu-mo-176-190965.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/marotta-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-cach-chieu-mo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/marotta-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-cach-chieu-mo-176-190965.html\">S\u1ebfp Juventus ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nGi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Marotta ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo, b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; c\u1ee7a Juventus m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mua Joao Cancelo ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/everton-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-hang-thai-barca-voi-gia-24-trieu-bang-180-190953.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/everton-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-hang-thai-barca-voi-gia-24-trieu-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/everton-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-hang-thai-barca-voi-gia-24-trieu-bang-180-190953.html\">Everton \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 24 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span><br>\r\nEverton mua Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, theo Goal, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Goodison Park \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 24 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4141","checkdouble":"190977"},{"date":"20:55 11/07","title":"N\u00d3NG: Arsenal ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 5","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/210541-4221396001_5807910584001_5807900029001-vs.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Lucas Torreira, c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt gi\u1edd Arsenal ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh n\u1eefa \u1edf phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Matteo Guendouzi t\u1eeb CLB Lorient (Ph\u00e1p).\r\n</h2><h2>Arsenal ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u00e2n binh&nbsp;Matteo Guendouzi</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt gi\u1edd, CLB Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ee9 5 trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018. \u0110\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao m\u1edbi 19 tu\u1ed5i, Matteo Guendouzi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ph\u00e1p, FC Lorient.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u00e2n binh Matteo Guendouzi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Arsenal ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u00e2n binh Matteo Guendouzi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/210541-4221396001_5807910584001_5807900029001-vs.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Matteo Guendouzi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Arsenal</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Matteo c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Lorient h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 10/2016 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 h\u01a1n 30 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ea7y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00ecnh l\u1ee5c l\u0103ng khi \u0111\u00e3 kinh qua c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb U18, U19 v\u00e0 U20 Ph\u00e1p.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau khi s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Matteo Guendouzi t\u1ea1i Arsenal. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb \u0111\u1ea7y t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u CLB. Nh\u01b0ng anh \u1ea5y t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a CLB&quot;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i Arsenal, Matteo s\u1ebd kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 29. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Guendouzi, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 cho Lorient kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n 8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, ng\u00f4i sao 19 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 5 c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u1edf phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018 sau Bernd Leno, Stephan Lichtsteiner, Sokratis Papastathopoulos v\u00e0 Lucas Torreira.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-117-xac-dinh-tuong-lai-gareth-bale-184-190977.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/9/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-117-xac-dinh-tuong-lai-gareth-bale.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-117-xac-dinh-tuong-lai-gareth-bale-184-190977.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 11/7: X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale</span><br>\r\nX\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale, Ed Woodward ch\u1ed1t t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3 cho M.U, Liverpool ra gi\u00e1 cho Messi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4140","checkdouble":"190980"},{"date":"22:16 11/07","title":"M.U nh\u1eadn tin vui t\u1eeb v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao Italia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/25/mu-nhan-tin-vui-tu-vu-lorenzo-pellegrini.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CLB Man United v\u1eeba nh\u1eadn tin vui t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Lorenzo Pellegrini khi l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB AS Roma m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>M.U nh\u1eadn tin vui t\u1eeb v\u1ee5 Lorenzo Pellegrini</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU nh\u1eadn tin vui t\u1eeb v\u1ee5 Lorenzo Pellegrini h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU nh\u1eadn tin vui t\u1eeb v\u1ee5 Lorenzo Pellegrini h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/1/MU-nhan-tin-vui-tu-vu-Lorenzo-Pellegrini-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n AS Roma b\u1eadt \u0111\u00e8n xanh v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Lorenzo Pellegrini</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 21, Lorenzo Pellegrini \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 Man United. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Roma v\u1edbi 37 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 28 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Serie A.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1edd s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, Pellegrini thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 ch\u1eefng ch\u1ea1c, t\u1ef1 tin n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa Roma. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f2n t\u1ecf ra hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 khi tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 4 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf La Liga m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 Lorenzo Pellegrini \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, CLB M.U \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u00e0i n\u0103ng n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin vui \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y khi gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao c\u1ee7a Roma, Monchi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Pellegrini ra \u0111i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd b\u00e1n \u0111i Dzeko, Kostas Manolas ho\u1eb7c Pellegrini. C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng tin nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt. \u0110\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y Roma v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y x\u1ea3y ra, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd xem x\u00e9t m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nghi\u00eam t\u00fac\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pellegrini gia nh\u1eadp AS Roma \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i t\u1eeb CLB Sassuolo. Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, anh \u0111ang thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 t\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Juventus, Manchester United v\u00e0 Arsenal.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-117-xac-dinh-tuong-lai-gareth-bale-184-190977.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/9/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-117-xac-dinh-tuong-lai-gareth-bale.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-117-xac-dinh-tuong-lai-gareth-bale-184-190977.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 11/7: X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale</span><br>\r\nX\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale, Ed Woodward ch\u1ed1t t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3 cho M.U, Liverpool ra gi\u00e1 cho Messi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-duoc-huong-loi-khi-ronaldo-gia-nhap-juventus-172-190982.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/9/20/chelsea-duoc-huong-loi-khi-ronaldo-gia-nhap-juventus.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-duoc-huong-loi-khi-ronaldo-gia-nhap-juventus-172-190982.html\">Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i khi Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus</span><br>\r\nSau khi Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus, CLB Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb L\u00e3o b\u00e0 th\u00e0nh Turin v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 hai ng\u00f4i sao Rugani va\u0300 Higuain.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chinh-thuc-so-huu-tan-binh-thu-5-172-190980.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/210541-4221396001_5807910584001_5807900029001-vs.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chinh-thuc-so-huu-tan-binh-thu-5-172-190980.html\">N\u00d3NG: Arsenal ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 5</span><br>\r\nSau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Lucas Torreira, c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt gi\u1edd Arsenal ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh n\u1eefa \u1edf phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Matteo Guendouzi t\u1eeb CLB...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4139","checkdouble":"190981"},{"date":"21:46 11/07","title":"Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i khi Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/9/20/chelsea-duoc-huong-loi-khi-ronaldo-gia-nhap-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus, CLB Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb 'L\u00e3o b\u00e0 th\u00e0nh Turin' v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 hai ng\u00f4i sao Rugani va\u0300 Higuain.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gonzalo Higuain cua Juventus\" title=\"Gonzalo Higuain cua Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/23/chelsea-sap-co-tien-dao-tri-gia-53-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB Juventus s\u1ebd b\u00e1n Higuain cho Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n mua Ronaldo</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB Real Madrid x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i qua 10/7. \u0110\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb Los Blancos, ph\u00eda Juve \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00ean t\u1edbi 105 tri\u1ec7u euro. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c cho m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u00e3 sang tu\u1ed5i 33.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c CR7 sang Italia, CLB Chelsea c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i t\u1eeb phi v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Theo gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u00dd, sau khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ronaldo, Bianconeri se\u0303 ba\u0301n hai c\u00e2\u0300u thu\u0309 Daniele Rugani va\u0300 Gonzalo Higuain cho Chelsea.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 100 tri\u1ec7u euro, trong \u0111\u00f3 Higuain c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00f2n Rugani v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 40 tri\u1ec7u. N\u1ebfu hai th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, L\u00e3o b\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu Ronaldo.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong th\u1eddi gian qua, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo s\u00e1t hai ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Juve. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 hai m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 HLV Maurizio Sarri mu\u1ed1n mang v\u1ec1 Stamford Bridge n\u00ea\u0301u \u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1\u0323c cho\u0323n thay th\u00ea\u0301 cho Antonio Conte \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-117-xac-dinh-tuong-lai-gareth-bale-184-190977.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/9/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-117-xac-dinh-tuong-lai-gareth-bale.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-117-xac-dinh-tuong-lai-gareth-bale-184-190977.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 11/7: X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale</span><br>\r\nX\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale, Ed Woodward ch\u1ed1t t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3 cho M.U, Liverpool ra gi\u00e1 cho Messi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chinh-thuc-so-huu-tan-binh-thu-5-172-190980.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/210541-4221396001_5807910584001_5807900029001-vs.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chinh-thuc-so-huu-tan-binh-thu-5-172-190980.html\">N\u00d3NG: Arsenal ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 5</span><br>\r\nSau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Lucas Torreira, c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt gi\u1edd Arsenal ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh n\u1eefa \u1edf phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Matteo Guendouzi t\u1eeb CLB...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sau-ronaldo-real-chia-tay-them-mot-ngoi-sao-180-190979.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/3/sau-ronaldo-real-chia-tay-them-mot-ngoi-sao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sau-ronaldo-real-chia-tay-them-mot-ngoi-sao-180-190979.html\">Sau Ronaldo, Real chia tay th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao</span><br>\r\nSau khi Real Madrid x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 Ronaldo sang Juve, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chia tay th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao kh\u00e1c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Achraf Hakimi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4138","checkdouble":"190982"},{"date":"22:36 11/07","title":"C\u1ef1c n\u00f3ng: Sao kh\u1ee7ng Serie A bay sang Anh k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i gia Premier League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/12/30/cuc-nong-sao-khung-serie-a-bay-sang-anh-ky-hop-dong-voi-dai-gia-premier-league.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jorginho c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Premier League l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra trong 24h t\u1edbi, theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n bay \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1edbi Anh k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jorginho sang Anh k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i gia Premier League</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec1 t\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o ch\u00ed khai th\u00e1c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Napoli, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc Serie A m\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jorginho c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Premier League Chelsea hay Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jorginho c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Premier League Chelsea hay Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/22/Jorginho-cap-ben-Premier-League-Chelsea-hay-Man-City-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea v\u00e0 Man City quan t\u00e2m Jorginho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y gi\u00fap anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, \u1edf Anh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-tao-ra-cu-soc-vu-muc-tieu-so-1-cua-man-city-172-190593.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Jorginho</span>, Man City c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMan City l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean quan t\u00e2m Jorginho, Pep mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Etihad nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho David Silva, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 32 tu\u1ed5i. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 l\u00e2u, song Man xanh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Man City v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Jorginho do v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n b\u1ea1c, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 44 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Napoli \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ee7 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y Chelsea c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Jorginho, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi \u0111\u1eadm mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJorginho c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Premier League l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra trong 24h t\u1edbi, theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n bay \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1edbi Anh k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n Man City v\u1ee5 Jorginho</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1nh ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p Jorginho \u1edf s\u00e2n bay, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1eafp l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Anh. \u0110i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Man City hay Chelsea m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jorginho sang Anh ky hop dong voi dai gia NHA\" title=\"Jorginho sang Anh k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i gia NHA\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/jo.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jorginho sang Anh k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i gia NHA</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jorginho nhieu kha nang se toi Chelsea\" title=\"Jorginho nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/jo-2.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jorginho nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Man City \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia. C\u00f3 2 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap The Blues gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t, Chelsea ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0 Napoli y\u00eau c\u1ea7u, th\u1ee9 2, Jorginho \u0111\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge theo ti\u1ebfng g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Sarri, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m thay Conte.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Mirror, t\u1ef7 ph\u00fa Roman Abramovich \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt g\u1eb7p ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Napoli, Aurelio De Laurentiis \u1edf Capri (Italia), sau cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp n\u00e0y Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Napoli nh\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, m\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a Jorginho b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1ea5m n\u00fat theo d\u00f5i Chelsea tr\u00ean Twitter, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e0ng cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn The Blues ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4137","checkdouble":"190983"},{"date":"14:44 11/07","title":"D\u00e0n sao Real tri \u00e2n Ronaldo","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/dan-sao-real-tri-an-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2> Ramos, Bale v\u00e0 Asensio b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3m ph\u1ee5c khi chia tay ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 \u1edf s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\"Nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang ta gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f9ng nhau \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. Anh \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh cho m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Real Madrid. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 CLB n\u00e0y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd qu\u00ean t\u00ean anh. Th\u1eadt l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t vinh d\u1ef1 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea1nh anh. M\u1ed9t c\u00e1i \u00f4m n\u1ed3ng th\u1eafm v\u00e0 ch\u00fac may m\u1eafn\", Sergio Ramos vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean Instagram ngay sau khi Real \u0111\u0103ng th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o chia tay Ronaldo.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u00e0n sao Real tri \u00e2n Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u00e0n sao Real tri \u00e2n Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Untitled-7110-1531267573.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ramos t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 ch\u00fac Ronaldo may m\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau khi c\u00f3 tin anh ra \u0111i. \u1ea2nh: Mail Online.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Real. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italy chi 126 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4la \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 33 tu\u1ed5i. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Serie A k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 Ronaldo s\u1ebd gi\u00fap v\u1ef1c d\u1eady gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eebng m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGareth Bale, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 5 n\u0103m s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh v\u00e0 t\u1eebng nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 v\u1edbi Ronaldo, vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean Instagram: \"M\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 phi th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 l\u00e0 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Th\u1eadt vinh d\u1ef1 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea1nh anh trong 5 n\u0103m qua. Ch\u00fac may m\u1eafn trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai nh\u00e9 b\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Marco Asensio cho r\u1eb1ng Ronaldo l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh m\u1eabu cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0 anh. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u00e0y t\u1ecf: \"Th\u1eadt l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t vinh d\u1ef1 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i c\u1ea1nh anh. Anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m g\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh. T\u00f4i ch\u00fac anh may m\u1eafn trong b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo \u0111\u00e3 ghi 450 b\u00e0n sau 438 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real, gi\u00e0nh b\u1ed1n Cup v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League v\u00e0 b\u1ed1n danh hi\u1ec7u La Liga sau 9 n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. </div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4136","checkdouble":"190947"},{"date":"13:38 11/07","title":"N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-4 U20 N\u1eef Australia (KT): Thua b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e0nh tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 khu v\u1ef1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/nu-viet-nam-vs-nu-australia-16h00-ngay-117.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung \u0111\u00e3 thua to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Australia \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018. Tuy\u1ebft Dung l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi c\u1ea3 hai b\u00e0n cho n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<h2>T\u1ed4NG H\u1ee2P: N\u1eee VI\u1ec6T NAM 2-4 U20 N\u1eee AUSTRALIA\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/11/Highlight-Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-U20-Nu-Australia.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nHI\u1ec6P 1<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y tuy\u1ec3n n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1eb7c trang ph\u1ee5c truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng m\u00e0u \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT TH\u1ee8 5: Hai \u0111\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 \u01b0u th\u1ebf c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n h\u01a1i nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 U20 n\u1eef Australia v\u1edbi th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1eef c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT TH\u1ee8 8: C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 U20 Australia v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd v\u00e0o t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kim Thanh th\u00ec N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1edbi tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi b\u00e0n thua\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/11/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-U20-Nu-Australia-08.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 17: N\u1eee VI\u1ec6T NAM M\u1ede T\u1ef6 S\u1ed0. D\u00f9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e9p v\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau pha ra ch\u00e2n hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c t\u1eeb ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m c\u1ee7a Tuy\u1ebft Dung, n\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam hi\u1ec7n nay.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/11/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-U20-Nu-Australia-16.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 18: U20 N\u1eee AUSTRALIA MAU CH\u00d3NG G\u1ee0 H\u00d2A. Tuy v\u1eady, l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i kho\u1ea3ng 1 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/11/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-U20-Nu-Australia-18.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 23: U20 N\u1eef Australia v\u1eabn \u0111ang d\u1ed3n \u00e9p c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 ra s\u1ee9c v\u00e2y h\u00e3m c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n Kim Thanh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 26: U20 N\u1eef Australia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t t\u1eeb c\u1ef1 ly kh\u00e1 xa nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e1 th\u1eb3ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng ch\u00fat n\u1eefa bay tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/11/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-U20-Nu-Australia-26.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 27: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u00fat xa t\u1eeb ph\u00eda U20 N\u1eef Australia v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng bay ch\u1ec7ch m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau trong gang t\u1ea5c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 29: N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u00e1 hay v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ph\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba U20 n\u1eef Australia. S\u1ed1 23 Ho\u00e0ng Qu\u1ef3nh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u1ebft th\u00fac cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng song th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee9u thua.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/11/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-U20-Nu-Australia-29.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 35: N\u1eee VI\u1ec6T NAM B\u1eca D\u1eaaN 1-2. S\u1ed1 21 c\u1ee7a U20 N\u1eef Australia, Nevin tung ra c\u00fa s\u00fat t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t xa nh\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng bay c\u1ef1c hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0o g\u00f3c cao v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kim Thanh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/11/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-U20-Nu-Australia-35.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 42: Sau khi b\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n, c\u00e1c c\u00f4 g\u00e1i c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c tri\u1ec3n khai t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00f2ng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a. Ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng h\u01a1n v\u00e0 g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n song kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t pha b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 s\u1eafc b\u00e9n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Hi\u1ec7p 1 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-2 d\u00e0nh cho U20 N\u1eef Australia. N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Tuy\u1ebft Dung nh\u01b0ng do s\u1ef1 thua k\u00e9m v\u1ec1 nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eb7t m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHI\u1ec6P 2<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Ngay sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1ea3i lao, n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u0103ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00f2ng s\u1edbm ghi b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang ta l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn song n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng s\u1edbm c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u00ec nguy c\u01a1 thua th\u00eam l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 52: QU\u00c1 \u0110\u00c1NG TI\u1ebeC. N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a nh\u01b0ng s\u1ed1 12 H\u1ea3i Y\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n U20 N\u1eef Australia trong pha \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/11/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-U20-Nu-Australia-52.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 60: N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e2m v\u00e0o b\u1ebf t\u1eafc khi \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i hi\u1ebfm hoi th\u00ec c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 64: M\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam tung ra c\u00fa s\u00fat t\u1eeb xa v